{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.1","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:1","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.002.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, impatients que nous \u00e9tions, et nous d\u00e9cidant \u00e0 rester seuls \u00e0 Ath\u00e8nes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.2","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.2.20","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.2.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.2","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:2","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>nous envoy\u00e2mes Timoth\u00e9e, notre fr\u00e8re, ministre de Dieu dans l\u2019\u00c9vangile de Christ, pour vous affermir et vous exhorter au sujet de votre foi,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.1","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.3","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:3","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>afin que personne ne f\u00fbt \u00e9branl\u00e9 au milieu des tribulations pr\u00e9sentes; car vous savez vous-m\u00eames que nous sommes destin\u00e9s \u00e0 cela.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.2","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.4","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:4","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et lorsque nous \u00e9tions aupr\u00e8s de vous, nous vous annoncions d\u2019avance que nous serions expos\u00e9s \u00e0 des tribulations, comme cela est arriv\u00e9, et comme vous le savez.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.5","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.5","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:5","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ainsi, dans mon impatience, j\u2019envoyai m\u2019informer de votre foi, dans la crainte que le tentateur ne vous e\u00fbt tent\u00e9s, et que nous n\u2019eussions travaill\u00e9 en vain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.6","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.4","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.6","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:6","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Joie et v\u0153ux de l\u2019ap\u00f4tre \u00e0 l\u2019occasion des nouvelles apport\u00e9es par Timoth\u00e9e<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-13: cf. Ac 18:5. (2 Co 7:4-7. 3 Jn 3, 4.) Ph 1:8-10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mais Timoth\u00e9e, r\u00e9cemment arriv\u00e9 ici de chez vous, nous a donn\u00e9 de bonnes nouvelles de votre foi et de votre charit\u00e9, et nous a dit que vous avez toujours de nous un bon souvenir, d\u00e9sirant nous voir comme nous d\u00e9sirons aussi vous voir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.7","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.5","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.7","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:7","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>En cons\u00e9quence, fr\u00e8res, au milieu de toutes nos calamit\u00e9s et de nos tribulations, nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 consol\u00e9s \u00e0 votre sujet, \u00e0 cause de votre foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.8","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.6","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.8","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:8","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Car maintenant nous vivons, puisque vous demeurez fermes dans le Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.9","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.7","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.9","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:9","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Quelles actions de gr\u00e2ces, en effet, nous pouvons rendre \u00e0 Dieu \u00e0 votre sujet, pour toute la joie que nous \u00e9prouvons \u00e0 cause de vous, devant notre Dieu!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.10","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.8","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.10","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:10","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Nuit et jour, nous le prions avec une extr\u00eame ardeur de nous permettre de vous voir, et de compl\u00e9ter ce qui manque \u00e0 votre foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.11","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.9","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.11","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:11","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Que Dieu lui-m\u00eame, notre P\u00e8re, et notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus, aplanissent notre route pour que nous allions \u00e0 vous!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.12","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.10","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.12","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:12","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Que le Seigneur augmente de plus en plus parmi vous, et \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de tous, cette charit\u00e9 que nous avons nous-m\u00eames pour vous,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.13","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.11","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.13","label":"","reference":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:13","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Thess.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Thess.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>afin d\u2019affermir vos c\u0153urs pour qu\u2019ils soient irr\u00e9prochables dans la saintet\u00e9 devant Dieu notre P\u00e8re, lors de l\u2019av\u00e8nement de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus avec tous ses saints!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.4.1","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.3.12","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fba3bdbf2.14116127');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba3bdbf2.14116127\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fba3bdbf2.14116127","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fba3bdbf2.14116127'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"http